<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</span></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b>There are just</b><b style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;<u>FOUR</u> days left to apply for work experience at The Challenge!</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b><u><br></u></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><img src="https://c.na8.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015C0000002axLa&amp;oid=00D80000000ZK1f&amp;lastMod=1430301690000" alt="Right click on the image to save it to your computer."></div><div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b>Here's a reminder of the details:</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">This summer, The Challenge is offering week-long work experience placements at our North London office to seven of the most dedicated NCS graduates from 2014. The opportunity to apply is open to those who have completed at least 16 hours of engagement with The Challenge Society in North or East London. That includes you!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div><font face="arial"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Successful applicants will have the opportunity to join The Challenge during our exciting period in the run-up to delivering NCS this summer. You'll have the chance to see behind the scenes and play a part in organising and delivering the programme to over 5000 young people in North and East London! This could range from making sure participants are ready for their NCS experience, helping&nbsp;</span>coordinate<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp; training of summer staff, or putting the final touches to how the programme will run.</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>How to apply:</b></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><u><b><br></b></u></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">If you are interested, please send a cover letter explaining why you would like to take part and a CV to <b>samuel.hepher@the-challenge.org</b>&nbsp;by<b> 11pm on Sunday 10th May</b>. Please also indicate in your cover letter which of the following weeks you would be available to take part:&nbsp;</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Monday 1st June - Friday 5th June</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Monday 22nd June - Friday 26th June</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Tuesday 28th July - Monday 3rd July (not including Saturday 1st and Sunday 2nd August)</span></li></ul><div><b>Assessment:</b></div><div><b><u><br></u></b></div><div>Candidates who pass the CV stage of application will then be invited to a two-hour group assessment on a weekday evening towards the end of May.</div><div><br></div><div>We look forward to receiving your application!</div><div><br></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><div><font face="arial">Sam Hepher</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Senior Assistant Programme Manager - The Challenge Society</font></div><div><font face="arial">The Challenge</font></div><div><font face="arial">Kentish Town Office</font></div><div><font face="arial">samuel.hepher@the-challenge.org</font></div><div><font face="arial">07785 623 399</font></div><div><font face="arial">020 3542 2400</font></div></div></div>]]></td>
